dct_title_s: Holly Beach City, Cape May Co., N.J. (Sheet 23)
dct_description_sm: "Aug. 1890." Includes key and text. Holly Beach City was incorporated into the newly created Wildwood City on Jan. 1, 1912. cf. Wikipedia. Historic Maps copy has sheets 22-23 of New Jersey coast series, vol 4., showing Holly Beach City, N.J. Historic Maps copy has stamp of Map Division, Library of Congress, dated Dec. 6, 1890.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn-Perris Map Co., Limited, 1890.
dct_subject_sm: Fire insurance maps—New Jersey—Holly Beach City—1890
